@node Main "FX guide"

  @{u}@{b}GUIDE FOR FX V1.11@{uu}@{ub}

Welcome to FX. In the following lines I want to explain special abilities of FX
and  how some things work. Please, read this guide carefully before starting it
the first time.


  @{" Copyright             " link "Copyright"}  legal stuff
  @{" Register              " link "Registrierung"}  FX is shareware!
  @{" What is FX?           " link "WhatIs"}  FX features
  @{" Installation          " link "Installation"}  how to install FX
  @{" Systemrequirements    " link "Systemanforderungen"}  hard- and software requirements
  @{" Usage                 " link "Benutzung"}  how to use FX
  @{" Thanks                " link "Danksagungen"}  special thanks to...
  @{" History               " link "Entstehungsgeschichte"}  FX history
  @{" Future                " link "Zukünftiges"}  planed things
  @{" Bugs                  " link "Bugs"}  nobody is perfect
  @{" Support               " link "support"}  Where to get updates
  The FX support has been greatly enhanced!
  @{" Author                " link "Autor"}  it's me

  @{" Index                 " LINK "Index"}  A quick overview
@endnode

